_sText:
This map is reupdated.
This was my first surf map with many bad things of around a year ago.
I now have lots more experience and made a version 2 because it was already a fun map.

I retextured it (also ramps) and added some npc's to give it a funny touch.
The ramps aren't buggy anymore.
I remade almost all ramps off the pro way wich made it now much easier to surf it.
Added some sound effects also near the npc's.
I remade the board in the beginning and it's optimized pretty much.


To make it short, it doesn't look anymore like a first surfmap. It still has his gameplay and the surf difficulty is low.
